The paper proposes measures to quantify the impact of research, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and data mining (cs.DL). The use of PageRank algorithm is also a common technique in web search and ranking, which falls under cs.IR. The paper also mentions eliminating self- and circular-citations, which is a topic related to network analysis (cs.SI) and graph theory (cs.CY). Finally, the application of these metrics to the InSpire database, which covers fundamental physics, suggests a possible connection to systems and control (cs.SY).
